        "text": "<p>Please provide the following documentation (if you haven't provided already) to complete the full application:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>SEPA Determination Letter (Required)</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Consent of Property Owner (Required)</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Project Plan Drawings (Required)</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Supporting Documents (Optional)</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Mitigation Plan(s) (Optional)</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p>If you do not have the documentation available at this point you will be provided the ability to upload them at a later time however, the Application will not be processed until all the information is provided and the application fees are paid.</p>",
